definition: tip/end/final stage/latter part/inessential detail/powder/dust/opera role of old man

sentences.english: Yet will I bring again the captivity of Moab in the latter days, saith the LORD.
sentences.chinese: 耶和華說，到末後，我還要使被擄的摩押人歸回。

sentences.english: The divisions of the camp of Judah went first, under their standard.
sentences.chinese: 在諸營末後的是但營的纛，按着軍隊往前行。

sentences.english: And the final condition of that man is worse than the first.
sentences.chinese: 那人末後的景況，比先前更不好了。

sentences.english: Eschatology is about ultimate things as well as "last" things.
sentences.chinese: 末世論是關於最終極和“末後”的事。
